 TaN lan2 ti7 chit-se3-kan long2 u7 tang7-taN3 tioh8 taN, iah8 u7-si5 teh siuN7 na7 taN lan2 ka-ti7 e5 taN3 chiu7 kau3-giah8; chong2-si7 Seng3-keng kong2, “ Lin2 tak8 lang5 e5 tang7-taN tioh8 saN-kang7 taN.” I3-su3 chiu7-si7 tioh8 chiong pat8 lang5 e5 taN3 kap lan2-e5 saN thin7. 
 U7 chit8-pai2 ti7 chin koaN5 e5 sou2-chai7 u7 nng7-e5 lang5 choe3-hoe2 teh kiaN5-lou7, in-ui7 hit-tiau5 lou7 u7 loh8-seh chin choe7, ti3-kau3 in koaN5-kau3 beh-si2, teh siuN7 m7-chai kiaN5 oe7 kau3 in sou2-ai3 khi3 e5 siaN5 iah be7, hut-jian5-kan khoaN3-kiN3 chit8-e5 lang5 to2 ti7 lou7-piN, phoa3-piN7 siong-tiong7, ia7 kio3 in tioh8 ho2-sim kiu3 i, ka7 i aiN7-kau3 un2-tong3 e5 sou2-chai7.
 In chit8-e5 m7-thiaN, kong2: “Goa2 chu7-ki2 to chiah-nih8 kan-khou2 kiaN5, thai2 oe7 koh aiN7 pat8-lang5 leh?” chong2-si7 koh chit8-e5 bo5 an2-ni siuN7 ka-ki7 e5 khun3-khou2 chiu7 kho2-lin5 i, hu5 i khi2-lai5, ka7 i aiN7 teh, chiu7 koh khi2-sin, sui-jian5 teh kiaN5 si7 chin ban7, m7-ku2 khah be7 kan-khou2, in-ui7 hit-lang5 e5 sin-khu aN3 ti7 i e5 kha-chiap-nih8 soa3 hou7 i m7-chai koaN5.
 Teh beh kau3 siaN5 e5 si5, hut-jian5 u7 khoaN3-tioh8 lang5 e5 sin-si ti7 lou7-piN, kin7 oa2-khi3 khoaN3 chiah jin7-tit si7 tu2-a2 i hit-e5 phoaN7 m7-ai3 tau3 aiN7 chit-e5 kan-khou2-lang5 e5, khi3 hou7 koaN5-si2 to2 ti7-hia, kai-chai3 chit-e5 ho2-sim the2-thiap lang5 e5 u7 tit-kiu3, an-jian5 kau3-ui7, in-ui7 i hoaN-hi2 ka7 pat8-lang5 tau3-saN-kang7. Kou3 ka-ki7 e5 lang5 i sou2 kiaN5 e5 lou7 khah siong5 si7 te7-it lan5-tit, iu7-koh i sou2 taN e5 taN3 ia7-si7 te7-it tang7; in-ui7 i bo5 eng7 pat8 lang5 e5 taN3 lai5 thin7-thau5. Ai3 lan2 ka-ki7-e5 khah khoai3 taN, tioh8 ke taN pat8 lang5-e5.
 Kiam2-chhai2 Siong7-te3 siuN2-su3 lan2 nng7 ki chhiu2 iah8 u7 chit ho7 e5 i3-su3 ti7-teh; chit8 ki hou7 lan2 koaN7 ka-ti7 e5 mih8, chit8 ki thang chan7 pat8 lang5. Iu7-koh lan2 siang-thau5 e5 pin2-taN tek-khak ia7 si7 an2-ni-siN; chit8 thau5 li2 e5 taN3, hit thau5 pat8 lang5-e5, “ Lin2 tak8 lang5 boh8-tit kou3 ka-ti7 e5 su7, ia7 tioh8 kou3 pat8 lang5 e5 su7 .”
